# Cloud Build upload filter for the web Cloud Run fallback (infra/web.Dockerfile).
# Unlike the default .gcloudignore (which excludes web/ because web normally ships
# via Firebase), this build COMPILES web/ inside Docker, so the source must upload.
# We still drop the heavy/derived dirs to keep the context small.
.git
.gcloudignore
infra/web.gcloudignore
node_modules/
web/node_modules/
web/dist/
**/__pycache__/
**/.venv/
**/*.tsbuildinfo
.env
*.key
